             Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd.
workers are considering a proposal by the Commission for
Conciliation, Mediation and Arbritration to resume talks over a
pay dispute, the National Union of Mineworkers said.   
 Members are choosing today between resuming talks or to
strike, NUM spokesman Lesiba Seshoka said from his mobile phone.
